time with my host family.

00:20:35.819 --> 00:20:38.905 position:50% align:center
[HIBIKI] Sounds good! Guess
we'll see you tomorrow, then!

00:20:38.988 --> 00:20:42.200 position:50% align:center
--[AKEMI] Have a good night!
--[AYAKA] See ya later!

00:20:42.283 --> 00:20:45.286 position:50% align:center
<i>Da svidanya,</i> Hibiki.

00:20:47.414 --> 00:20:51.418 position:50% align:center
[HIBIKI] I'm home!
Today was so exhausting!

00:20:51.501 --> 00:20:56.172 position:50% align:center
Wha--? Why would we have
