became uncomfortably clear.

00:20:59.467 --> 00:21:01.469 position:50% align:center
[HIBIKI panting]

00:21:02.512 --> 00:21:04.556 position:50% align:center
Welcome home, host <i>sestra</i> !

00:21:04.639 --> 00:21:06.266 position:50% align:center
