00:21:06.349 --> 00:21:07.851 position:50% align:center
[HIBIKI groans]

00:21:07.934 --> 00:21:11.104 position:50% align:center
[HIBIKI] I guess we were due
for some sort of twist.

00:21:11.187 --> 00:21:14.983 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] I don't know how
to respond to all that?

00:22:45.407 --> 00:22:48.952 position:50% align:center
Hey there, guys! Today let's
try momentum-based training!

00:22:49.035 --> 00:22:51.287 position:50% align:center
We already worked on
chin-ups earlier today.

00:22:51.371 --> 00:22:53.164 position:50% align:center
Now we're going to work
on some jump-pushups

00:22:53.248 --> 00:22:54.499 position:50% align:center
that you can do anywhere!

00:22:54.582 --> 00:22:57.210 position:50% align:center
It's just a normal pushup
with a jump added in.

00:22:57.293 --> 00:22:58.503 position:50% align:center
=Does this look familiar?

