If you have an apartment,

00:23:04.134 --> 00:23:06.678 position:50% align:center
then choose an appropriate
time and place to do these.

00:23:06.761 --> 00:23:09.973 position:50% align:center
Watch your shoulders. Your
form is very important here.

00:23:10.056 --> 00:23:12.809 position:50% align:center
Careful! Always keep your elbows
slightly bent when you land.

00:23:12.892 --> 00:23:14.602 position:50% align:center
This will relieve
a lot of pressure.

00:23:14.686 --> 00:23:16.104 position:50% align:center
Don't push yourself too hard.

00:23:16.187 --> 00:23:18.064 position:50% align:center
You can start on your
knees if you need to.

00:23:18.148 --> 00:23:21.818 position:50% align:center
Your goal is ten reps.
Ready? Go!

00:23:21.901 --> 00:23:24.863 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI] If it's too hard, you
can modify on your knees!

00:23:24.946 --> 00:23:28.283 position:50% align:center
[AYAKA] Find a safe tempo,
and keep that rhythm!

00:23:28.366 --> 00:23:30.577 position:50% align:center
[MACHIO]
Five! Six!

00:23:30.660 --> 00:23:33.955 position:50% align:center
Harasho! Don't give up!

00:23:34.039 --> 00:23:36.833 position:50% align:center
