This is... the last one!

00:23:36.916 --> 00:23:39.836 position:50% align:center
[GIRLS cheering, laughing]

00:23:39.919 --> 00:23:41.296 position:50% align:center
Be consistent with this.

00:23:41.379 --> 00:23:43.256 position:50% align:center
And I guarantee you'll see
more results than you would

00:23:43.340 --> 00:23:44.758 position:50% align:center
with regular pushups!

00:23:44.841 --> 00:23:46.593 position:50% align:center
And always remember kids...

00:23:46.676 --> 00:23:49.679 position:50% align:center
[ALL] ...true strength
comes from within!